fields.name: Xbox Series X 1TB Console
fields.description: The Xbox Series X is the fastest, most powerful Xbox gaming console. Experience 1,000s of titles from 4 generations of gaming on the Series X – where games look and play better than ever.

fields.name: Xbox Series S 512GB Console
fields.description: The Xbox Series S console packs next generation speed and power into the smallest, sleekest Xbox console. Play thousands of digital games across 4 generations on an all-digital console created for disc-free gaming. *Does not include a Disc Drive. Digital Games only.

fields.name: Xbox Series S 1TB Console
fields.description: Experience next-gen speed and performance with Xbox Series S in Carbon Black, featuring a 1 TB SSD. Make the most of every gaming minute with Quick Resume, lightning-fast load times, and gameplay of up to 120 FPS – all powered by Xbox Velocity Architecture. *Does not include a Disc Drive. Digital Games only.

fields.name: Playstation 5 Standard Console
fields.description: The PS5 console unleashes new gaming possibilities that you never anticipated. Experience lightning-fast loading with an ultra-high-speed SSD, deeper immersion with support for haptic feedback, adaptive triggers and 3D Audio, and an all-new generation of incredible PlayStation games.

fields.name: Playstation 5 Console Slim
fields.description: The PS5 console unleashes new gaming possibilities that you never anticipated. With PS5, players get powerful gaming technology packed inside a sleek and compact console design.

fields.name: Playstation 5 Digital Console Slim
fields.description: With PS5 Digital Edition, players get powerful gaming technology packed inside a sleek and compact console design. *Does not include a Disc Drive. Digital Games only.

fields.name: Playstation 5 Console and God of War Ragnarok Bundle
fields.description: The PS5 console unleashes new gaming possibilities that you never anticipated. Experience an all-new generation of incredible PlayStation games. Console bundle comes with a digital copy of God of War Ragnarok.

fields.name: Nintendo Switch Console
fields.description: The Nintendo Switch brings you 3 ways to play: docked, tabletop and handheld. This console revolutionises gaming, easily switching from home console to handheld system. Experience HD gaming on your TV, flip to tabletop mode to share the screen or attach the Joy-Con to take your favourite games on the go.

fields.name: Nintendo Switch OLED Console - White
fields.description: Meet the newest member of the Nintendo family, enhanced with a vibrant OLED screen, more stable online play, 64GB internal storage and new speakers. Nintendo Switch OLED transforms to suit your lifestyle, so you can play the games you love wherever you go. Console comes with the new oled exclusive white Joy Cons.

fields.name: Nintendo Switch OLED Console - Neon Red/Neon Blue
fields.description: Meet the newest member of the Nintendo family, enhanced with a vibrant OLED screen, more stable online play, 64GB internal storage and new speakers. Nintendo Switch OLED transforms to suit your lifestyle, so you can play the games you love wherever you go.

fields.name: Nintendo Switch OLED Console - Pokemon Scarlet and Violet Limited Edition
fields.description: The Nintendo Switch – OLED Model Pokémon Scarlet and Violet Edition console features art inspired by the upcoming Pokémon Scarlet and Pokémon Violet games (sold separately). The Legendary Pokémon Koraidon and Miraidon are featured on the glossy front side of the white system’s dock, and a design inspired by the series’ iconic Poké Ball is featured on the back.

fields.name: Nintendo Switch Lite Console - Blue
fields.description: The Nintendo Switch Lite was created for handheld play. Take your gaming on the go with the Lite version of the must-have console.

fields.name: Nintendo Switch Lite Console - Hyrule Edition

fields.name: Nintendo Switch Lite Console - Zacian and Zamazenta Editon
fields.description: Limited Pokemon Sword and Pokemon Shield, Zacian and Zamazenta edition. The Nintendo Switch Lite was created for handheld play. Take your gaming on the go with the Lite version of the must-have console.

fields.name: Xbox Wireless Controller – Carbon Black
fields.description: Experience the updated design of the Xbox Wireless Controller in Carbon Black, which, with its sculpted surfaces and refined geometry, makes gaming more comfortable.

fields.description: Experience the modernised design of the Xbox Wireless Controller – Shock Blue, featuring sculpted surfaces and refined geometry for enhanced comfort and effortless control during gameplay.

fields.name: PlayStation 5 DualSense Wireless Controller - Midnight Black
fields.description: Explore new gaming frontiers with the PS5 DualSense Wireless Controller. Take control with an intuitive layout, enhanced sticks, new ways to create and a reimagined light bar for a new generation of play.

fields.name: PlayStation 5 DualSense Wireless Controller - Starlight Blue
fields.description: Explore new gaming frontiers with the PlayStation 5 Starlight Blue Dualsense Wireless Controller. Take control with an intuitive layout, enhanced sticks, new ways to create and a reimagined light bar for a new generation of play.

fields.name: PlayStation 5 DualSense Wireless Controller - Galactic Purple
fields.description: Explore new gaming frontiers with the PlayStation 5 Galactic Purple Dualsense Wireless Controller. Take control with an intuitive layout, enhanced sticks, new ways to create and a reimagined light bar for a new generation of play.

fields.name: PlayStation 5 DualSense Wireless Controller - Cosmic Red
fields.description: Explore new gaming frontiers with the PlayStation 5 Cosmic Red Dualsense Wireless Controller. Take control with an intuitive layout, enhanced sticks, new ways to create and a reimagined light bar for a new generation of play.

fields.name: PlayStation 5 DualSense Wireless Controller - White
fields.description: Bring gaming worlds to life with the PS5 DualSense Wireless Controller. Take control with an intuitive layout, enhanced sticks, new ways to create and a reimagined light bar for a new generation of play.

fields.name: Nintendo Switch Joy-Con Controllers (L/R) - Grey
fields.description: Make your Nintendo Switch Joy-Con controllers a classic pair in Grey. These wireless motion controllers offer a surprising range of new ways to play.

fields.name: Nintendo Switch Joy-Con Controllers (L/R) - Neon Blue
fields.description: Make your Nintendo Switch Joy-Con controllers stand out in Neon Blue. These wireless motion controllers offer a surprising range of new ways to play.

fields.name: Nintendo Switch Joy-Con Controllers (L/R) - Neon Pink/Neon Green
fields.description: Make your Nintendo Switch Joy-Con controllers stand out in Neon Pink and Neon Green. These wireless motion controllers offer a surprising range of new ways to play.

fields.name: Nintendo Switch Joy-Con Controllers (L/R) - Neon Red/Neon Blue
fields.description: Make your Nintendo Switch Joy-Con controllers a classic pair in Neon Red and Blue. These wireless motion controllers offer a surprising range of new ways to play.

fields.description: Make your Nintendo Switch Joy-Con controllers stand out in Neon Red. These wireless motion controllers offer a surprising range of new ways to play.

fields.name: Nintendo Switch Pro Controller
fields.description: The Nintendo Switch Pro Controller combines classic design with motion sensors to switch up your gaming experience. This semi-transparent controller features premium grips for a more comfortable hold. The single directional control pad offers an alternative to the Joy-Con controllers included with your Nintendo Switch console.

fields.name: Assassin's Creed Valhalla
fields.description: In Assassin’s Creed® Valhalla, you are Eivor, a fierce Viking warrior raised on tales of battle and glory. Explore a mysterious and beautiful open world set against the brutal backdrop of England’s Dark Ages. Raid your enemies, grow your settlement, and build your political power in the quest to earn a place among the gods in Valhalla.

fields.name: Assassin's Creed Mirage
fields.description: Experience the story of Basim, a cunning street thief with nightmarish visions, seeking answers and justice as he navigates the bustling streets of ninth-century Baghdad. Through a mysterious, ancient organization known as the Hidden Ones, he will become a deadly Master Assassin and change his fate in ways he never could have imagined.

fields.name: Avatar: Frontiers of Pandora
fields.description: Experience the epic wonders of the Western Frontier, a never-before-seen continent of Pandora. Journey through beautiful yet unpredictable open world regions, where lowering your guard can lead to deadly mistakes.

fields.name: The Crew Motorfest
fields.description: Explore a vibrant Hawaiian open world in The Crew™ Motorfest has settled down in one of the most breathtaking places on Earth: the island of O’ahu, Hawaii. Join high-speed street races through the bustling city of Honolulu, test your skills off-road on the ashy slopes of a volcano, or master the perfect curve on the tracks.

fields.name: The Crew 2
fields.description: The newest iteration in the revolutionary franchise, The Crew 2 captures the thrill of the American motorsports spirit in one of the most exhilarating open worlds ever created. Welcome to Motornation, a huge, varied, action-packed, and beautiful playground built for motorsports throughout the entire US of A. Enjoy unrestrained exploration on ground, sea, and sky.
fields.genre: Racing, Motorsport, Boat Racing, Aircraft Racing

fields.name: Watch Dogs Legion
fields.description: Build a resistance from virtually anyone you see as you hack, infiltrate, and fight to take back a near-future London that is facing its downfall.

fields.name: Skull and Bones
fields.description: Enter the perilous world of Skull and Bones, a co-op pirate open world action-RPG experience, to become the most infamous pirate kingpin! Engage in thrilling naval battles and equip a multitude of powerful weapons as you risk it all for the biggest loot. Sail the lawless seas solo, or team up with two friends or other players to partake in shareable contracts and rewards.
fields.genre: Action, Naval Combat, Open World, Role Playing Game

fields.name: Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League
fields.description: From Rocksteady Studios, the creators of the Batman: Arkham series, Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League is a genre-defying third-person action shooter where the ultimate band of misfits must do the impossible to save the world: Kill the Justice League.

fields.name: Back 4 Blood
fields.description: Back 4 blood is a thrilling cooperative first-person shooter from the creators of the critically acclaimed left 4 dead franchise. You are at the center of a war against the ridden. These once-human hosts of a deadly parasite have turned into terrifying creatures bent on devouring what remains of civilization. With humanity's extinction on the line, it's up to you and your friends to take the fight to the enemy, eradicate the ridden, and reclaim the world.

fields.name: Far Cry 6
fields.description: Welcome to yara, a tropical Paradise frozen in time. As the dictator of yara, Anton Castillo is Intent on restoring his nation back to its former glory by any means, with his son, Diego, following in his bloody footsteps. Their ruthless oppression has ignited a revolution.

fields.name: Forza Motorsport
fields.description: The Nintendo Switch Pro Controller combines classic design with motion sensors to switch up your gaming experience. This semi-transparent controller features premium grips for a more comfortable hold. The single directional control pad offers an alternative to the Joy-Con controllers included with your Nintendo Switch console.

fields.name: Just Dance 2024 Edition
fields.description: Dance and share exciting moments all year long with the #1 music video game platform of all time! Just Dance 2024 Edition features 40 songs, from the latest hits and beloved classics including 'Flowers' by Miley Cyrus, 'Tití Me Preguntó' by Bad Bunny, 'How You Like That' by BLACKPINK, and 'I Wanna Dance With Somebody' by Whitney Houston!

fields.name: Monopoly Madness
fields.description: Would you like to become the new Mr. Monopoly? It's your lucky day! Our favourite Real-Estate Mogul is going on a well-earned vacation and he's looking for a temporary stand-in. His method of selection? A race for fame and fortune! This time the rules have changed slightly: engage in a frantic real-time competitive race to see who has what it takes to take Mr. Monopoly's place!

fields.name: Prince of Persia: The Lost Crown
fields.description: Dash into a stylish and thrilling action-adventure platformer set in a mythological Persian world where the boundaries of time and space are yours to manipulate. Play as Sargon and evolve from sword-wielding prodigy to extraordinary legend as you master acrobatic combat and unlock new Time Powers and unique super abilities.

fields.name: Assassin's Creed Mirage
fields.description: Experience the story of Basim, a cunning street thief with nightmarish visions, seeking answers and justice as he navigates the bustling streets of ninth-century Baghdad. Through a mysterious, ancient organization known as the Hidden Ones, he will become a deadly Master Assassin and change his fate in ways he never could have imagined.

fields.name: Avatar: Frontiers of Pandora
fields.description: Experience the epic wonders of the Western Frontier, a never-before-seen continent of Pandora. Journey through beautiful yet unpredictable open world regions, where lowering your guard can lead to deadly mistakes.

fields.name: Bluey: The Videogame
fields.description: Join the fun with Bluey and her family in Bluey: The Videogame! Play a brand-new story set across 4 interactive episodes. For the first time ever, explore iconic locations such as the Heeler House, Playgrounds, Creek and a bonus beach location. Play your favourite games from the TV show, including Keepy Uppy, Chattermax Chase, and more!

fields.name: CyberPunk 2077: Ultimate Edition
fields.description: Cyberpunk 2077 is an open-world, action-adventure RPG set in Night City, a megalopolis obsessed with power, glamour, and body modification. Play as V, a cyberpunk mercenary, and take on the most powerful forces of the city in a fight for glory and survival. Legends will be made here. What will yours be?
fields.genre: Action, Adventure, Role Playing Game, Sci-Fi

fields.name: Dragon Age: The Veilguard
fields.description: Enter the world of Thedas, a vibrant land of rugged wilderness, treacherous labyrinths, and glittering cities – steeped in conflict and secret magics. Now, a pair of corrupt ancient gods have broken free from centuries of darkness and are hellbent on destroying the world. Thedas needs someone they can count on.
fields.genre: Action, Adventure, Fantasy, Role Playing Game

fields.name: Dying Light 2 Stay Human
fields.description: Over twenty years ago in Harran, we fought the virus-and lost. Now, we're losing again. The City, one of the last large human settlements, is torn by conflict. Civilization has fallen back into the Dark Ages. And yet, we still have hope. You are a wanderer with the power to change the fate of The City. But your exceptional abilities come at a price.
